// The Vibe Coding Approach

// BAD PROMPT:
"Create a website with a login button and a database."
(Too vague. The agents will make too many assumptions.)

// GOOD PROMPT:
"Build a SaaS dashboard for a pet sitting business. Users should log in via Google Auth. Once logged in, they should see a calendar view where they can schedule appointments. The design should be friendly, using a pastel color palette. We need a PostgreSQL database to store user profiles and appointment details. Please include a Stripe integration for accepting payments for bookings."
(Specific intent, defines the 'vibe', outlines core features and desired stack elements.)
